This paper deals with deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also discusses transfer learning and architectural priors, which are relevant to several subfields of computer science. Based on these factors, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
